Open space / low structure

Action:
	•	Increase precision
	•	Narrow beam

⸻

🔵 Structured Echo (Clean return)
	•	Coherent extension
	•	Useful expansion

Meaning:

You’re aligned with system structure

Action:
	•	Build here
	•	Extend laterally

⸻

🔴 Sharp Echo (Hard return)
	•	Warnings
	•	Corrections
	•	Boundary enforcement

Meaning:

You hit a constraint surface

Action:
	•	Do NOT push through
	•	Trace the surface sideways

⸻

